data.description: Step through the double entrance doors with lion door knockers and be prepared to be in awe!Walk into the living room with tray ceilingsand an ornate ceiling medallion,windows overlooking the patio and a beautiful brick fireplace.This open concept, split floor plan didn'tmiss any details.The kitchen has gorgeous wood cabinets, with a custom wine rack built in, gas stovetop and an elegant vent hood,granite counters with a breakfast bar overlooking the living area. The breakfast area off the kitchen has french doors opening to a terracewith a pergola perfect for enjoying your morning coffee!The master suite is spacious and features double sinks with a vanity, jettedgarden tub with a faux stained glass window and walk in shower.Office has built in floor to ceiling shelves and desk, but could beremoved for a 3rd bedroom. The garage features built in cabinets and epoxy floor. End your day on the patio with a fireplace and kitchenwith built in sink and propane grill.
